                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Re-opened - is_readable() broke BC (see ZF-2232)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-11-25T14:57:53.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-11-25T14:57:53.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/17698",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "To fix this, we'll have to use Zend_Loader::isReadable() which will obviously introduce a dependency for Zend_Config that isn't there at the moment.\n\n\nCode would be:\n{code}\n        if (!Zend_Loader::isReadable($filename)) {\n            throw new Zend_Config_Exception('Unable to read config file');\n        }\n{code}\n\n\nThoughts?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-11-25T15:00:50.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-11-25T15:00:50.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/17699",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=doctorrock83",
                        "name": "doctorrock83",
                        "displayName": "julien PAULI",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Yes Rob, that's the patch I think.\nI forgot about that *** include path ;-)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=doctorrock83",
                        "name": "doctorrock83",
                        "displayName": "julien PAULI",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-11-25T15:09:18.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-11-25T15:09:18.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/17736",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Won't fix in 1.x as we don't want to introduce a BC break by using is_readable() or introduce a dependency on Zend_Loader.\n\nWorkaround if the notice is a problem is to call Zend_Loader::isReadable() before called Zend_Config_Ini\/Zend_Config_Xml.\n\n\nRegards,\n\n\nRob...",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-11-27T14:24:46.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-11-27T14:24:46.000+0000"
